node.text:
Share your couple tips 💕

📌Color My Mood: a cute activity journal for tracking your feelings. 

📣Please note that there're two edition for this book, US edition (hardcover with stickers), UK edition (paperback).

📣Is it available worldwide？
These book is available especially in Amazon, in addition to local booksellers and some bigger chains. You can always check your regular Amazon, you will likely be able to find the book. If not, you can check with local bookshops to request it too.

node.text:
Today, I'm excited to share with you that my second book is here! 🥳

I'm really grateful for this experience and a big thanks to my publisher @sterlingbooks @sterlingkids & @dandcbooks and the team for making this book possible 💕💕💕

Special thanks to all of you who follow and read my comics. Thank you for being a part of my Bichi Mao Comic journey *hugs*

📌Color My Mood: a cute activity journal for tracking your feelings. 

📣Please note that there're two edition for this book, US edition (hardcover with stickers), UK edition (paperback). (Read page 3 for more information)

📣Is it available worldwide？
These book is available especially in Amazon, in addition to local booksellers and some bigger chains. You can always check your regular Amazon, you will likely be able to find the book. If not, you can check with local bookshops to request it too.
